cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses a system for media access control in online social networks, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR). The system is designed to work with media contents, which can be images, videos, or other multimedia formats (cs.MM). The system also involves data management and storage, which can be related to database systems (cs.DB). The system is designed to work with diverse attributes of data consumers, which can be related to social informatics (cs.SI). Finally, the system involves mobile devices, which can be related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
